&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Project Manager (PMO) is responsible for leading and executing complex business projects while ensuring strategic alignment and adherence to technical standards. This role requires strong technical expertise, leadership, and the ability to drive projects independently with minimal oversight.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COLLECTIVE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comply with the HALA’s code of conduct and ethics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote the HALA’s vision, mission, values and model desired behaviors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote HALA and spread its culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commit to HALA’s rules and regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform tasks as directed in the pursuit of the achievement of organizational goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share with team know-how and encourage their development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB-SPECIFIC&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and execute complex business projects, ensuring alignment with strategic objectives and technical standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply advanced business &amp;amp; technical knowledge to oversee integrations, server configurations, and cybersecurity measures for payment solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and guide project teams, setting clear expectations, and promoting a culture of excellence and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and refine project management frameworks, employing best practices tailored to the payments industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating closely with the Head of Enterprise and demonstrating significant autonomy in decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embody a strong sense of leadership and ownership, acting decisively and effectively without the need for frequent oversight.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
